com.siperian.sif.message.metadata

Class MetaDataParameter

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.siperian.sif.message.metadata.MetaDataBase
      • com.siperian.sif.message.metadata.MetaDataParameter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    MetaDataInputParameter, MetaDataOutputParameter

    public class MetaDataParameter
extends MetaDataBase
    Represents metadata about the parameter of a cleanse function or mapping. This class is the base class for MetaDataInputParameter and MetaDataOutputParameter. Those classes are present for use by Castor and should not be referenced directly as they do not contain any additional properties or methods.
    See Also:
    DescribeSiperianObjectRequest, Serialized Form

    API Group: Metadata
